{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a2c4a7c52","title":"关于旅大地区的三点指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f11ffdecef","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"8a2c4a7c52"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"cce608ea44","name":"林彪","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"55648699f2","type":"title","text":"关于旅大地区的三点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8a2c4a7c52"},{"id":"f1ffdbc198","type":"paragraph","text":"一、军队无论如何不能开枪，防止坏人挑拨我们开枪犯错误，千万不要上当。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8a2c4a7c52"},{"id":"0a36d52bcd","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要继续克服资产阶级派性，一定要—碗水端平，不要支—派、压一派。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8a2c4a7c52"},{"id":"b8c872cd40","type":"paragraph","text":"三、当前特别重要的是继续抓好工人队伍工作，有了军队，有了工人阶级，有就能稳定局势，我们什么都不怕。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8a2c4a7c52"},{"id":"b1e7e2a15c","type":"paragraph","text":"（据五月十三日海军新党委给海工红团电报）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8a2c4a7c52"},{"id":"509bc40b2f","type":"paragraph","text":"摘自北大《北斗星》","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8a2c4a7c52"}],"page":{"id":"d4a84046ca","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8a2c4a7c52","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}